S3Encryption.Description: Encryption configuration for uploading artifacts to S3

IgnoreCoordinates.Description: List of coordinates of rectangles to be ignored during visual testing

ScreenshotName.Description: Name of the screenshot to be used as base reference for visual testing

ActiveTracing.Description: Enable active tracing if set to true

MemoryInMB.Description: Provide maximum memory available for canary in MB

TimeoutInSeconds.Description: Provide maximum canary timeout per run in seconds

EncryptionMode.Description: Encryption mode for encrypting artifacts when uploading to S3. Valid values: SSE_S3 and SSE_KMS.

KmsKeyArn.Description: KMS key Arn for encrypting artifacts when uploading to S3. You must specify KMS key Arn for SSE_KMS encryption mode only.

Key.Description: The key name of the tag. You can specify a value that is 1 to 127 Unicode characters in length and cannot be prefixed with aws:. You can use any of the following characters: the set of Unicode letters, digits, whitespace, _, ., /, =, +, and -.

Value.Description: The value for the tag. You can specify a value that is 1 to 255 Unicode characters in length and cannot be prefixed with aws:. You can use any of the following characters: the set of Unicode letters, digits, whitespace, _, ., /, =, +, and -.

BaseCanaryRunId.Description: Canary run id to be used as base reference for visual testing

BaseScreenshots.Description: List of screenshots used as base reference for visual testing

ArtifactS3Location.Description: Provide the s3 bucket output location for test results

DeleteLambdaResourcesOnCanaryDeletion.Description: Deletes associated lambda resources created by Synthetics if set to True. Default is False

ExecutionRoleArn.Description: Lambda Execution role used to run your canaries

FailureRetentionPeriod.Description: Retention period of failed canary runs represented in number of days

StartCanaryAfterCreation.Description: Runs canary if set to True. Default is False

SuccessRetentionPeriod.Description: Retention period of successful canary runs represented in number of days

VisualReference.Description: Visual reference configuration for visual testing
